Subject: Secunia Research: GIGABYTE Dldrv2 ActiveX Control Array Indexing Vulnerability

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 15/07/2010

   - GIGABYTE Dldrv2 ActiveX Control Array Indexing Vulnerability -

====================================================================== 
